# =============================================================================
# Ash-NLP v5.0 Environment Variables Template
# =============================================================================
# FILE VERSION: v5.0-5-1.0-1
# LAST MODIFIED: 2026-01-01
# CLEAN ARCHITECTURE: v5.1 Compliant
# Repository: https://github.com/the-alphabet-cartel/ash-nlp
